metadata.name: Xyberpunk Hideouts Gold #1
metadata.description:
Limited Gold Edition 1 of 10 exclusively only on Foundation!

Not the ordinary NFT that you know. Xyberpunk Hideouts is a collection of unique digital illustrated sci-fi / futuristic artwork processed via generative adversarial network (GAN). Each artwork is uniquely created using an on-chain generative process that augmented from machine learning (ML) model in which two neural networks compete with each other to generates unique artifacts based masterpiece. 

It’s unique in a way where each NFT does not have a similarity base like any other NFT but still maintaining the theme of it’s original art. 

Own a hideout today and get your Xybercity access which includes GAN workshop, NFT academy and alphas.
